column2:
"...It seems they've finally defeated Dark Falz...
How's the plan coming along?"

"Third Plan Progress: 98%.
Photon Sensitivity: 99% of projected levels."

"Tomorrow will mark five hundred years...
It won't be long now until the Day of Arrival."
"Correction: The Day of Arrival will be in 31,415,926 seconds. Margin of error: Plus or minus 0.05--"
"Plan continuation accepted. Transferring to the next phase."
